Comment: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino is in charge of things in general,
Comment: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm the MC and also responsible for the sound systems.
Comment: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The vice president will be in charge of the lighting,
Comment: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and the secretary is working with the catering.
Comment: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got minions from the soccer club taking care of all the other odd jobs.
Comment: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and also, someone very intimidating coming to handle any wardrobe mishaps!
Comment: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Does she mean Kawasaki?
Comment: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes it sound like she hired Yakuza or something...
Comment: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hikigaya and Yuigahama will be helping us out, then...
Comment: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps they could cover the reception desk or do lights or music?
Comment: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work at the reception desk! Hikky really isn't suited for it...
Comment: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So true.
Comment: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The reception desk isn't the place for me.
Comment: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can be the sound assistant.
Comment: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was for me to do it alone, but I have to be all over the place tonight.
Comment: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'd be a huge help if you could stay the whole time.
Comment: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After the letters were washed away
Comment: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Testing, testing... Testing, testing...
Comment: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Testing, testing...
Comment: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya.
Comment: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we'll use to give you cues.
Comment: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That takes me back.
Comment: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this other one to Isshiki.
Comment: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Comment: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Does the mic need a stand?
Comment: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I believe so.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How high do you need it? About here?
Comment: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect, but I can handle something like this on my own.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right. My bad.
Comment: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's nothing to apologize for.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I mean, for other things, too...
Comment: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the fact I'm helping today, things just kind of went in that direction.
Comment: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out it wasn't feasible for me to remain totally uninvolved.
Comment: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's understandable. Isshiki also relies on your help.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to have grown up a bit lately, so eventually she won't need me anymore, yeah?
Comment: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, I won't be doing any more jobs like this.
Comment: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Comment: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think that she'd let you escape so easily.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a scary way to put it. Yikes, that's a terrifying thought!
Comment: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Comment: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone depends on you, you'll always save them.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. Depends on the time and circumstance.
Comment: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work out there!
Comment: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Here's your headset.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, thanks!
Comment: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you two don't need an interpreter anymore.
Comment: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Yukino were just conversing normally, right?
Comment: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, We don't need any intepretation when we're talking about work.
Comment: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at ordinary conversation and chitchat, but talking business is my specialty.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's not much to brag about...
Comment: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guys like that do exist.
Comment: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who only get motivated to talk when it's about business.
Comment: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that.
Comment: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guys out there need excuses like that to talk with girls. Sad, right? So stop it.
Comment: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In my experience, guys like that suddenly start calling me by name after we talk just three times.
Comment: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then around the fifth time, they invite me to hang out.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After that comes a confession, and that's when I stopped bothering to talk with them at all.
Comment: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it, stop it!
Comment: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, stop! What's going on? Did you go to the same junior high as me?
Comment: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't. But as I recall, that's the excuse you used to...
Comment: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait a minute!
Comment: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you just been using business as a pretext to get close to me and were planning on confessing soon?
Comment: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and were planning on confessing soon?
Comment: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,và có dự định thú nhận sớm không?
Comment: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind hanging out, but anything
Comment: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond that we'll have to wait until all of this is over. I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, when this is all over. So do your job. If you don't it'll never end.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me. Not another guy who doesn't listen...
Comment: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And for your information, none of this means that I hate working or anything!
Comment: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually quite enjoy times like these, you know?
Comment: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is a certain delight that can only be found behind the scenes.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna do it again next year?
Comment: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be throwing next year's prom for ME, you know.
Comment: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean prom... I mean the Service Club.
Comment: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something to ask the club president.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no authority whatsoever when it comes to club activities.
Comment: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the club itself will be gone.
Comment: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there's no reason for me to do any more... work.
Comment: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda got that feeling. But...
Comment: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't really matter, does it?
Comment: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean it doesn't matter?
Comment: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can help out even if you aren't part of a club.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how you get involved.
Comment: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even do it as a student council member.
Comment: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we have a position open right now...
Comment: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go and talk with Yukinoshita. She's totally into that sort of thing, I think.
Comment: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to do that.
Comment: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to extend the offer to Yui, too.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We should all do it together!
Comment: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous. There's only one position, right?
Comment: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I'll fire the vice president.
Comment: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rude...
Comment: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I think that would be the most realistic path forward.
Comment: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting caught up in the irresistibly cute demands of your cute junior,
Comment: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and ultimately settling with a convenient relationship like this isn't so bad, right?
Comment: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an awfully tempting suggestion.
Comment: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, something like that may have been the most ideal.
Comment: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll provide you with the perfect excuse, if you want.
Comment: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If Isshiki came to me, completely serious and honest,
Comment: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked for help with the student council
Comment: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then I wouldn't be able to refuse and she likely knows that.
Comment: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, she just tried to coax an answer out of me instead...
Comment: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a seriously good person.
Comment: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I?!
Comment: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not seem like it, but I'm all sorts of convenient!
Comment: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to consider that proposal with an open mind.
Comment: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's basically code for "absolutely not."
Comment: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that does sound like you, though.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Comment: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yukinoshita.
Comment: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be proceeding as scheduled, please get ready.
Comment: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting the guests in now.
Comment: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, roger that! I'm putting on some tunes for the crowd!
Comment: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikky, nice work!
Comment: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too. Are you done at the reception desk?
Comment: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't think anybody would be showing up this late.
Comment: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn for a break.
Comment: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, things are winding down now.
Comment: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I really worked up an appetite.
Comment: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you decide on a wish yet?
Comment: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nothing has really come to mind just yet. How about you?
Comment: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... everything I wished for before has basically been granted.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten basically everything I asked for.
Comment: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping with the prom, Komachi's present... Oh, I forgot about hanging out somewhere.
Comment: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go somewhere after the final exam?
Comment: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the exam...
Comment: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But that would be a good source of motivation!
Comment: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any other wishes, feel free to let me know about them.
Comment: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Okay then, maybe I'll ask for one more wish...
Comment: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,May I please have this dance?
Comment: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Đùa th
Comment: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't that sort of dance, right?
Comment: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, you're right! Ah, I'm embarrassed!
Comment: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have your hand?
Comment: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's not that sort of dance?
Comment: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who brought it up!
Comment: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you're having fun.
Comment: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of wish is hard to grant.
Comment: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! I won't ask again.
Comment: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one will be the last, 'kay?
Comment: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to prepare for the final address, so please take care of the rest.
Comment: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, have fun out there.
Comment: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki, are you ready?
Comment: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting in the wings! I'm all ready!
Comment: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking off my headset now!
Comment: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just standby until you hear them call you up.
Comment: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am! See you later!
Comment: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là PA
Comment: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll cue the ending with a sign instead of via headset.
Comment: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't miss it.
Comment: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see me?
Comment: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can see you just fine.
Comment: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But, where are you right now? In the audience?
Comment: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Above you, look up. Come on, I knew you've been looking this way the whole time.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm just not used to the idea of looking up at you.
Comment: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're used to looking down on me then?
Comment: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to being looked down on so it doesn't really matter to me, though.
Comment: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That subservient disposition is about the only thing I actually look up to you for.
Comment: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I have to look up so high it hurts my neck and shoulders.
Comment: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not big enough for shoulder pain. Though I won't specify what part of you...
Comment: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say something?
Comment: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't hear you, can you say it again?
Comment: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything. The song is gonna end soon.
Comment: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikigaya...
Comment: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect you to grant that wish.
Comment: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Comment: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Let's end it with this.
Comment: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job. It was a nice prom.
Comment: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you were here, you should've joined in.
Comment: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My time to shine is at the farewell ceremony. I'm the guest of honor.
Comment: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna get a chance to dance at that ceremony.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. It's a shame. I wanted to dance with you, too.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw us?
Comment: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good event.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your cooperation in this matter.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your guidance, we were able to hold the event with no major problems.
Comment: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it was a huge help that you were able to accommodate our sudden requests.
Comment: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job as the person in charge.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You served in that position very well. I'm quite impressed.
Comment: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun watching, too! It was so great!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray for you, Yukino!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is the type of thing you want to do, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking into following this sort of career path, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of career? What do you mean by that?
Comment: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you ask her yourself?
Comment: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,About that... I have an interest in Dad's job,
Comment: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'd like to be involved at some point in the future.
Comment: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the work I did for this event doesn't directly relate to that future.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I also know it proves nothing. Honestly, I'm not expecting anything immediate,
Comment: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about far off in the future.
Comment: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make you fully aware of what my current thoughts are.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are seriously considering this, right?
Comment: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings about it, Yukino.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're absolutely serious about pursuing this, then I will support you.
Comment: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time to think about everything from here on out.
Comment: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush your decisions.
Comment: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already getting late. It's time for me to leave.
Comment: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, thank you for everything.
Comment: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mom certainly seemed like she was okay with it.
Comment: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to say how other people feel though, right?
Comment: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking us?
Comment: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at the very least, I'm not satisfied.
Comment: 0,0:13:58.78,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly accept that this outcome has the same value as my twenty years of experience.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want me to yield my position,
Comment: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're going to have to show me something worthwhile.
Comment: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After all those years I spent being groomed,
Comment: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't expect me to just give up so nonchalantly.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to realize that it's going to be difficult to appease me.
Comment: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, perhaps I'll go say hello to Shizuka and then head home.
Comment: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Comment: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister went and said all those weird things...
Comment: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always saying weird things. I'm used to it already.
Comment: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Comment: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm glad that you said that. But...
Comment: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she was a little serious today.
Comment: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how much those twenty years are weighing upon her.
Comment: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that the year that you spent,
Comment: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or rather the year that we all spent, weighs just as heavily.
Comment: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the length of time that matters.
Comment: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean our time spent together was so bizarre!
Comment: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bizarre?
Comment: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it WAS bizarre. The Service Club has been a weird place from the start.
Comment: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of that is your fault, though.
Comment: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure. But that's also why it was so much fun!
Comment: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's because you were always so weird that there were also
Comment: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,sad, uncomfortable, and painful times...
Comment: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, other times were way more fun and happier.
Comment: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long and amazing time that I really came to love.
Comment: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Comment: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say that I agree with confidence.
Comment: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why... If we're going to bring this to an end, I think now is the best time.
Comment: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Với tớ thì cứ tiếp tục như vậy cũng không sao..
Comment: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you want it, then that's fine with me.
Comment: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! We already finished cleaning up the gym, so... Huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Comment: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Comment: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already done?
Comment: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Cleaning this room is all that's left.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, thanks for all your help!
Comment: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good work, everyone. I'm leaving.
Comment: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... This room still needs to be cleaned...
Comment: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, wait!
Comment: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I just thought I should tell you...
Comment: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help today.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just for what you did today. For everything you've done up to now.
Comment: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all of the trouble I've caused you.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't something to apologize for.
Comment: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about trouble, I caused quite a bit more of it.
Comment: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just say we're even in that regard.
Comment: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough, you really were a handful.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can agree that we're even.
Comment: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, thank you. You have helped me so much.
Comment: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's all... okay now.
Comment: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, I'll work hard to... do better on my own.
Comment: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why-
Comment: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. It's fine.
Comment: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Comment: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...
Comment: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd just run away.
Comment: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you're the one who called me out.
Comment: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say that? What is it you're trying to achieve here?
Comment: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. It doesn't matter to me, whichever one is fine.
Comment: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care what's going on in my family.
Comment: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care whether it's me or Yukino who ends up doing it.
Comment: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is for you to leave me satisfied. Give me some sort of ending.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, do you want to see sincerity?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I'm being mugged for my feelings instead of my wallet.
Comment: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not far from the truth.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But just like me, my mother won't accept any of this either.
Comment: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed so positive about it, though.
Comment: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,None of what happened is enough to satisfy that woman,
Comment: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which is why she didn't say yes or no.
Comment: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality is that there has been zero resolution.
Comment: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seemed to me like Yukino had her own realization.
Comment: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's the benefit of being family.
Comment: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who was watching should be able to tell, not just me and my mother.
Comment: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even people who are "just friends" like you must have noticed it.
Comment: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hard for me to say because I'm not sure
Comment: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we get along well enough to be considered friends.
Comment: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an amazing answer to hear so late in the game.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly do not know when to give up.
Comment: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely no one would be satisfied by that.
Comment: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chào!
Comment: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it impossible?
Comment: 0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Comment: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The wish that she made was nothing but an act of compensation.
Comment: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino, you, and Gahama all did your best to accept it, right?
Comment: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You only kneaded the shape and the words around, and looked away from it...
Comment: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it... That's enough. I already know all of this.
Comment: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You did good at giving excuses and rationalizing...
Comment: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you decieved yourselves and avoided the reality.
Comment: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew all along. I talked big by calling it "a man's pride,"
Comment: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, what I'm doing now is no different from what I did before.
Comment: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's much worse than before.
Comment: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I also coerced both of them into swallowing that incredibly outrageous lie.
Comment: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you...
Comment: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get drunk.
Comment: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I can't.
Comment: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't settle this properly, then it's just going to smolder away in you.
Comment: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much time passes, it will never end.
Comment: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done my own share of deceiving for twenty years now, so I know all too well...
Comment: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My entire life has been nothing but a sham.
Comment: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hikigaya...
Comment: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if anything genuine... actually exists.
Comment: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Comment: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go outside with your indoor shoes!
Comment: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to lock up. Hurry up and change your shoes.
Comment: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya...
Comment: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already late so I'll take you home.
Comment: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to. I have my bike with me.
Comment: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's fine.
Comment: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave your bike here, leave it here!
Comment: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsushiba!
Comment: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Homerun
Comment: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Comment: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hori!
Comment: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburo!
Comment: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Satozaki! Fukuura!
Comment: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Otsuka! Morozumi!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she only saying the names of former all-star Marines members?
Comment: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Franko!
Comment: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Haruno tell you anything?
Comment: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, lots of things.
Comment: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She says I can't get drunk. Just like her.
Comment: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is true for Haruno, but... You're not talking about alcohol, are you?
Comment: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she means more of like a mood or a relationship. According to her, I'm codependent.
Comment: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly does sound like what Haruno would say.
Comment: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that some people could agree with Haruno's take
Comment: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if they were looking at things from a place of skepticism.
Comment: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not one of those people.
Comment: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You, and Yukinoshita, and Yuigahama do not have that sort of relationship.
Comment: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't summarize what you have in a simple word like "codependence."
Comment: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you honestly pack all of your feelings into just a single word?
Comment: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about it? Do you feel a little better after some exercise?
Comment: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.65,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,You're gonna need a better pick up line than that if you wanna hook up with any athletes.
Comment: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.57,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,You aren't cute, you know.
Comment: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:49.41,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,But I am truly grateful to you for being so considerate of me.
Comment: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.62,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry for being a burden right to the end.
Comment: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:56.41,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,That's totally fine! I'm your teacher, after all.
Comment: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:00.17,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,Now then, ready to get started?
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.71,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,This will be my final lesson to you.
